<Window x:Class="AreaParty.windows.InitSetting"
        xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
        xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
        xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/blend/2008"
        xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006"
        xmlns:sys= "clr-namespace:System;assembly=mscorlib"
        xmlns:local="clr-namespace:AreaParty.windows"
        WindowStartupLocation="CenterScreen"
        mc:Ignorable="d"
        Background="{x:Null}"
        ResizeMode="NoResize"
        Icon="/styles/skin/ico/ico_settingpage_setting.png"
        FontFamily="NSimSun" 
        TextOptions.TextFormattingMode="Display"
        Title="初始化设置" Height="500" Width="800" Closing="Window_Closing">
    <Window.Resources>
        <LinearGradientBrush x:Key="MyBrush" EndPoint="0.5,1" StartPoint="0.5,0">
            <GradientStop Color="#CFFFFFFF"/>
            <GradientStop Color="#FF7EBDD8" Offset="1"/>
        </LinearGradientBrush>
        <Style x:Key="ThisLabel" TargetType="Label">
            <Style.Triggers>
                <Trigger Property="IsMouseOver" Value="True">
                    <Setter Property="Foreground" Value="Gray"></Setter>
                </Trigger>
            </Style.Triggers>
        </Style>
        <Style x:Key="ThisButton" TargetType="{x:Type Button}">
            <Setter Property="Template">
                <Setter.Value>
                    <ControlTemplate TargetType="{x:Type Button}">
                        <Grid>
                            <Rectangle x:Name="bg" Stroke="Black" StrokeThickness="0" Visibility="Visible">
                                <Rectangle.Fill>
                                    <ImageBrush ImageSource="/styles/skin/Button/btbg.png" Stretch="Uniform"/>
                                </Rectangle.Fill>
                            </Rectangle>
                            <Rectangle x:Name="fg" Stroke="Black" StrokeThickness="0" Visibility="Hidden" RadiusX="0" RadiusY="0">
                                <Rectangle.Fill>
                                    <ImageBrush ImageSource="/styles/skin/Button/btfg.png" Stretch="Uniform"/>
                                </Rectangle.Fill>
                            </Rectangle>
                            <TextBlock x:Name="textBlock" HorizontalAlignment="Center" Margin="0" TextWrapping="Wrap" Text="{TemplateBinding Content}" d:LayoutOverrides="Height" VerticalAlignment="Center" Foreground="#FF020F5C"/>
                        </Grid>
                        <ControlTemplate.Triggers>
                            <Trigger Property="IsDefaulted" Value="True"/>
                            <MultiTrigger>
                                <MultiTrigger.Conditions>
                                    <Condition Property="IsMouseOver" Value="True"/>
                                </MultiTrigger.Conditions>
                                <Setter
						Property="Visibility" TargetName="fg" Value="Visible"/>
                            </MultiTrigger>
                            <Trigger Property="IsPressed" Value="True"/>
                            <Trigger Property="IsEnabled" Value="False"/>
                        </ControlTemplate.Triggers>
                    </ControlTemplate>
                </Setter.Value>
            </Setter>
        </Style>
    </Window.Resources>
    <Grid >
        <Grid.Background>
            <ImageBrush ImageSource="/styles/skin/background/SettingWindowBackGround.jpg"/>
        </Grid.Background>
        <Grid.Effect>
            <DropShadowEffect BlurRadius="8" ShadowDepth="0" Color="#FF5C8185" Opacity="0.25" Direction="225"/>
        </Grid.Effect>
        <Grid.RowDefinitions>
            <RowDefinition></RowDefinition>
        </Grid.RowDefinitions>
        <Grid Name="RemoteSetting" >
            <Grid.RowDefinitions>
                <RowDefinition Height="30"/>
                <RowDefinition/>
                <RowDefinition Height="40"/>
            </Grid.RowDefinitions>
            <Label Name="ContentTitle" Background="#B2DFEE" Content="远程桌面初始化设置" Foreground="BlueViolet" HorizontalContentAlignment="Center" Grid.Row="0" HorizontalAlignment="Left" FontWeight="Bold" Width="800"/>
            <Grid  Grid.Row="1">

                <TextBlock  FontSize="16"   TextBlock.LineHeight="23" TextWrapping="Wrap" xml:space="preserve">
为了使用远程桌面功能，以便您可以在电视上使用PC软件，需要进行如下设置，您可以跳过此设置，稍后在设置选项自行设置。
                </TextBlock>
                <TextBlock  FontSize="17" Foreground="#4F94CD" Margin="0,55,0,0" FontWeight="Heavy"  TextBlock.LineHeight="23" FontStretch="Expanded"    TextWrapping="Wrap" xml:space="preserve">
PC端设置步骤：
                </TextBlock>
                <TextBlock  FontSize="16" Margin="0,85,0,0" FontFamily="幼圆" TextBlock.LineHeight="23" TextWrapping="Wrap" xml:space="preserve">
1. 右键我的电脑，选择属性。
2. 选择远程设置。
3. 勾选允许远程协助连接这台计算机和允许远程连接到此计算机，其他不要勾选，确定即可。
                </TextBlock>
                <TextBlock  FontSize="17"  Margin="0,160,0,0" Foreground="#4F94CD" FontWeight="Heavy"  TextBlock.LineHeight="23"    TextWrapping="Wrap" xml:space="preserve">
TV端设置步骤(建议插上鼠标键盘方便设置)：
                </TextBlock>
                <TextBlock  FontSize="16" Margin="0,195,0,0" FontFamily="幼圆" TextBlock.LineHeight="23" TextWrapping="Wrap" xml:space="preserve">
1. 在TV已安装应用中打开RD Client应用，选择上面添加按钮（即右上角加号），然后选择Desktop选项。
2. 点击Scan/Scan again选项，搜索局域网可用设备，搜索结果显示的列表中，选择本PC的计算机名称，选择Enter every time，继续选择Add user account，在弹出的界面分别输入本PC用户名和密码，选择save保存。
3. 在返回的界面选择右上方CONNECT，然后在弹出界面继续选择CONNECT，即可测试远程桌面功能能否正确使用。
                </TextBlock>
            </Grid>
            <Grid Grid.Row="2">
                <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                    <ColumnDefinition  Width="585"></ColumnDefinition>
                    <ColumnDefinition Width="100"></ColumnDefinition>
                    <ColumnDefinition Width="100"></ColumnDefinition>
                </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                <Label Content="更多图文设置>" Name="RDP_Label" Style="{DynamicResource ThisLabel}" MouseLeftButtonDown="Label_More_Click"></Label>
                <Button Name="Button_Finish" Margin="2,0,2,0" Content="下一步" Style="{DynamicResource ThisButton}" Grid.Column="1" Click="Button_Finish_Click"></Button>
                <Button Name="Button_Skip" Margin="2,0,2,0" Content="稍后设置" Style="{DynamicResource ThisButton}" Grid.Column="2" Click="Button_Skip_Click"></Button>
            </Grid>
        </Grid>


        <Grid Name="GameSetting" Grid.Row="0" Visibility="Collapsed"  >
            <Grid.RowDefinitions>
                <RowDefinition Height="30"/>
                <RowDefinition/>
                <RowDefinition Height="40"/>
            </Grid.RowDefinitions>
            <Label Name="GameSettingTitle" Background="#B2DFEE" Content="游戏串流设置" Foreground="BlueViolet" HorizontalContentAlignment="Center" Grid.Row="0" HorizontalAlignment="Left" FontWeight="Bold" Width="800"/>
            <TextBlock Name="ContentTextGame"  FontFamily="幼圆" FontSize="17" TextBlock.LineHeight="23" FontStretch="Expanded"  Padding="5,0,5,0" Grid.Row="1" TextWrapping="Wrap" xml:space="preserve">
    为了您可以在TV直接玩电脑上的游戏，需要您进行如下设置，您可以跳过此设置，稍后在设置选项自行设置。注意，此功能需要硬件支持，要求独立显卡GTX600以上，具体请查询英伟达官网。
            </TextBlock>
            <TextBlock  FontFamily="幼圆" FontSize="17" TextBlock.LineHeight="23" FontStretch="Expanded" Margin="0,55,0,0" Padding="5,0,5,0" Grid.Row="1" TextWrapping="Wrap" xml:space="preserve">
1.  打开Geforce Experience(如果没有安装此程序请上官网下载安装)，然后进行帐号注册或者使用第三方帐号登录。
2.  选择上方设置按钮，然后选择SHIELD，在此界面，将GAMESTREAM选项打开即可。
            </TextBlock>
            <Grid Grid.Row="2">
                <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                    <ColumnDefinition  Width="585"></ColumnDefinition>
                    <ColumnDefinition Width="100"></ColumnDefinition>
                    <ColumnDefinition Width="100"></ColumnDefinition>
                </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                <Label Content="更多图文设置>" Name="Game_Label" Style="{DynamicResource ThisLabel}" MouseLeftButtonDown="Label_More_Click"></Label>
                <Button  Margin="2,0,2,0" Content="下一步" Style="{DynamicResource ThisButton}" Grid.Column="1" Click="Button_Finish_Click"></Button>
                <Button  Margin="2,0,2,0" Content="稍后设置" Style="{DynamicResource ThisButton}" Grid.Column="2" Click="Button_Skip_Click"></Button>
            </Grid>
        </Grid>
        <Grid Name="ScreenSetting" Grid.Row="0" Visibility="Collapsed" >
            <Grid.RowDefinitions>
                <RowDefinition Height="30"/>
                <RowDefinition/>
                <RowDefinition Height="40"/>
            </Grid.RowDefinitions>
            <Label Name="ScreenSettingTitle" Background="#B2DFEE" Content="投屏设置" Foreground="BlueViolet" HorizontalContentAlignment="Center" Grid.Row="0" HorizontalAlignment="Left" FontWeight="Bold" Width="800"/>
            <ScrollViewer VerticalScrollBarVisibility="Auto" Grid.Row="1" HorizontalScrollBarVisibility="Disabled" Style="{DynamicResource for_scrollviewer}" Background="{x:Null}">
                <Grid>
                    <TextBlock   FontSize="17" TextBlock.LineHeight="23" FontStretch="Expanded"  Padding="5,0,5,0" Grid.Row="1" TextWrapping="Wrap" xml:space="preserve">
    本软件需要电脑、手机还有电视都安装AreaParty软件，为了使用全部功能，需要进行如下配置，您也可以不做设置，依然可以使用本软件，只是部分功能不可用，您也可以跳过本次设置，稍后在软件设置界面进行设置。
                    </TextBlock>
                    <TextBlock   FontSize="17" Margin="0,75,0,0" FontWeight="Heavy"  Foreground="#4F94CD"  TextBlock.LineHeight="23" FontStretch="Expanded"  Padding="5,0,5,0" Grid.Row="1" TextWrapping="Wrap" xml:space="preserve">
    a．打开手机和电视AreaParty软件
                    </TextBlock>
                    <TextBlock   FontSize="17" Margin="0,100,0,0" FontWeight="Heavy" Foreground="#4F94CD"  TextBlock.LineHeight="23" FontStretch="Expanded"  Padding="5,0,5,0" Grid.Row="1" TextWrapping="Wrap" xml:space="preserve">
    b．选择要设置的屏幕
                    </TextBlock>
                    <TextBlock   FontSize="16" Margin="0,125,0,0"  FontFamily="幼圆" TextBlock.LineHeight="23" FontStretch="Expanded"  Padding="5,0,5,0" Grid.Row="1" TextWrapping="Wrap" xml:space="preserve">
    点击下方立即设置按钮，在弹出的窗口我们会自动搜索安装了我们AreaParty软件的电视，选择所需设置的电视，然后选择下一步。
                    </TextBlock>
                    <TextBlock   FontSize="17" Margin="0,170,0,0" FontWeight="Heavy" Foreground="#4F94CD"  TextBlock.LineHeight="23" FontStretch="Expanded"  Padding="5,0,5,0" Grid.Row="1" TextWrapping="Wrap" xml:space="preserve">
    c．游戏设置
                    </TextBlock>
                    <TextBlock   FontSize="16" Margin="0,195,0,0"  FontFamily="幼圆" TextBlock.LineHeight="23" FontStretch="Expanded"  Padding="5,0,5,0" Grid.Row="1" TextWrapping="Wrap" xml:space="preserve">
    为了将电脑上游戏投影到电视上，需要开启此功能。此功前一项游戏投影设置开启才可继续设置，此功能需硬件支持，显卡GTX600以上。开启开关，选择下一步，如果本电脑支持此功能，将会在右下角有个配对弹窗，需要输入电视上显示的配对码。
                    </TextBlock>
                    <TextBlock   FontSize="17" Margin="0,270,0,0" FontWeight="Heavy"  Foreground="#4F94CD" TextBlock.LineHeight="23" FontStretch="Expanded"  Padding="5,0,5,0" Grid.Row="1" TextWrapping="Wrap" xml:space="preserve">
    d．无线投屏设置
                    </TextBlock>
                    <TextBlock   FontSize="16" Margin="0,295,0,0"  FontFamily="幼圆" TextBlock.LineHeight="23" FontStretch="Expanded"  Padding="5,0,5,0" Grid.Row="1" TextWrapping="Wrap" xml:space="preserve">
    如果需要使用特殊模式(MIRACAST)将PC显示桌面投屏到电视，则需要设置此选项，否则特殊模式将不起作用，注，此功能需要因特尔的无线网卡。
        1.打开电视上无线投屏接收软件（Miracast接收端），待本软件中显示接收端后，选择然后进入初始化连接设置。
        2.初始化连接设置。按住win+K，然后选择刚才选择接收端，完成第一次连接。
        3.完成设置（部分设备无法自动连接，请用户按照步骤2手动连接）。
                    </TextBlock>

                </Grid>
            </ScrollViewer>
            <Grid Grid.Row="2">
                <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                    <ColumnDefinition  Width="585"></ColumnDefinition>
                    <ColumnDefinition Width="100"></ColumnDefinition>
                    <ColumnDefinition Width="100"></ColumnDefinition>
                </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                <Label Content="更多图文设置>" Name="SoftWare_Label" Style="{DynamicResource ThisLabel}" MouseLeftButtonDown="Label_More_Click"></Label>
                <Button  Margin="2,0,2,0" Content="立即设置" Style="{DynamicResource ThisButton}" Grid.Column="1" Click="Button_Finish_Click"></Button>
                <Button  Margin="2,0,2,0" Content="稍后设置" Style="{DynamicResource ThisButton}" Grid.Column="2" Click="Button_Skip_Click"></Button>
            </Grid>
        </Grid>
        <Grid Name="LoginSetting" Grid.Row="0" Visibility="Collapsed" >
            <Grid.RowDefinitions>
                <RowDefinition Height="30"/>
                <RowDefinition/>
                <RowDefinition Height="40"/>
            </Grid.RowDefinitions>
            <Grid.Effect>
                <DropShadowEffect BlurRadius="8" ShadowDepth="0" Color="#FF5C8185" Opacity="0.25" Direction="225"/>
            </Grid.Effect>
            <Label Name="LoginSettingTitle" Background="#B2DFEE" Content="服务器连接设置" Foreground="BlueViolet" HorizontalContentAlignment="Center" Grid.Row="0" HorizontalAlignment="Left" FontWeight="Bold" Width="800"/>
            <Grid  Grid.Row="1">
                <Grid.RowDefinitions>
                    <RowDefinition Height="40"/>
                    <RowDefinition ></RowDefinition>
                </Grid.RowDefinitions>
                <Label Content="服务器连接开关" Foreground="#cc9966" FontFamily="宋体" HorizontalAlignment="Left" VerticalAlignment="Center"/>
                <CheckBox Name="LoginCheckBox" Style="{DynamicResource OrangeSwitchStyle}" Click="Login_CheckBox_Click"  HorizontalAlignment="Right" VerticalAlignment="Top"  Margin="0,6,6,0"/>
                <TextBlock Grid.Row="1" Name="LoginTextBlock" TextWrapping="Wrap"  FontSize="17" TextBlock.LineHeight="23"   FontStretch="Expanded"  xml:space="preserve">
    若开启长连接，当你打开本软件的时候会直接连上服务器，之后可以使用手机远程控制PC进行P2P下载文件功能;好友共享的文件下载;查看下载状态。
    若不开启长连接，则不能使用以上功能，想重新打开请前往设置管理中的服务连接界面进行进行设置。
                </TextBlock>
            </Grid>
            <Grid Grid.Row="2">
                <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                    <ColumnDefinition  Width="585"></ColumnDefinition>
                    <ColumnDefinition Width="100"></ColumnDefinition>
                    <ColumnDefinition Width="100"></ColumnDefinition>
                </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                <Label Content="更多图文设置>" Name="LongConnect_Label" Style="{DynamicResource ThisLabel}" MouseLeftButtonDown="Label_More_Click"></Label>
                <Button  Margin="2,0,2,0" Content="下一步" Style="{DynamicResource ThisButton}" Grid.Column="1" Click="Button_Finish_Click"></Button>
                <Button  Margin="2,0,2,0" Content="稍后设置" Style="{DynamicResource ThisButton}" Grid.Column="2" Click="Button_Skip_Click"></Button>
            </Grid>
        </Grid>
        <Grid Name="NasSetting" Grid.Row="0" Visibility="Collapsed" >
            <Grid.RowDefinitions>
                <RowDefinition Height="30"/>
                <RowDefinition/>
                <RowDefinition Height="40"/>
            </Grid.RowDefinitions>
            <Grid.Effect>
                <DropShadowEffect BlurRadius="8" ShadowDepth="0" Color="#FF5C8185" Opacity="0.25" Direction="225"/>
            </Grid.Effect>
            <Label Name="NasSettingTitle" Background="#B2DFEE" Content="NAS连接设置" Foreground="BlueViolet" HorizontalContentAlignment="Center" Grid.Row="0" HorizontalAlignment="Left" FontWeight="Bold" Width="800"/>
            <Grid  Grid.Row="1">
                <Grid.RowDefinitions>
                    <RowDefinition Height="40"/>
                    <RowDefinition ></RowDefinition>
                </Grid.RowDefinitions>
                <Label Content="NAS连接开关" Foreground="#cc9966" FontFamily="宋体" HorizontalAlignment="Left" VerticalAlignment="Center"/>
                <CheckBox Name="LoginCheckBox_NAS" Style="{DynamicResource OrangeSwitchStyle}" Click="Login_CheckBox_NAS_Click"  HorizontalAlignment="Right" VerticalAlignment="Top"  Margin="0,6,6,0"/>
                <TextBlock Grid.Row="1" Name="NasTextBlock" TextWrapping="Wrap"  FontSize="17" TextBlock.LineHeight="23"   FontStretch="Expanded"  xml:space="preserve">
    若开启长连接，当你打开本软件的时候会直接连上服务器，之后可以使用手机远程管理NAS，进行数据存储、查看状态等操作。
    若不开启长连接，则不能使用以上功能，想重新打开请前往设置管理中的NAS连接界面进行进行设置。
                </TextBlock>
            </Grid>
            <Grid Grid.Row="2">
                <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                    <ColumnDefinition  Width="585"></ColumnDefinition>
                    <ColumnDefinition Width="100"></ColumnDefinition>
                    <ColumnDefinition Width="100"></ColumnDefinition>
                </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                <Label Content="更多图文设置>" Name="NasLongConnect_Label" Style="{DynamicResource ThisLabel}" MouseLeftButtonDown="Label_More_Click"></Label>
                <Button  Margin="2,0,2,0" Content="下一步" Style="{DynamicResource ThisButton}" Grid.Column="1" Click="Button_Finish_Click"></Button>
                <Button  Margin="2,0,2,0" Content="稍后设置" Style="{DynamicResource ThisButton}" Grid.Column="2" Click="Button_Skip_Click"></Button>
            </Grid>
        </Grid>
    </Grid>
</Window>
